Boolean SnpCreateUIResourceSpec::run (  ) 

Functional part of this snippet.

Create a resource-specifications string that defines an assortment of user-interface components.

Pass the resource-specification string to the constructor of a Window object, then define the behavior of the elements created by the resource specification.

Returns:
True if the snippet ran as expected, false otherwise
